de.team33.libs.exceptional.v4.functional

Class Conversion

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.team33.libs.exceptional.v4.functional.Conversion

  • public final class Conversion
extends Object
    A utility class that can convert certain functional constructs that may throw checked exceptions (e.g. XFunction) into more common constructs (e.g. Function) that will wrap such exceptions in WrappedExceptions.
    See Also:
    Converter
